{"tid":1491623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成立「監警公署」清算所有黑警！！！","createTime":"2019-08-20T13:22:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T14:04:01.000Z","uid":171094,"like":27,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b17a14c386702ae1c187fb33a7a7ed1540c11136","tid":1491623,"uid":171094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:22:49.000Z","msg":"之前都有巴打開過post<br />\n<br />\n會唔會將要求成立「監警公署」取代獨立調查委員會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1313824\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1313824</a><br />\n<br />\n亦都有人寫過文講過呢個 idea<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/122030\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F122030&d=TRt9Hu9y5T%2Bqj71zgJeH9hV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=328fdf6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/122030</a><br />\n<br />\n我同大家都有過疑慮就係<br />\n呢個署向特首負責咪又係會變icac，一撚樣冇辦法令人相信<br />\n<br />\n之後諗諗下<br />\n既然大家都認同成立有調查權、檢控權嘅獨立調查委員會係最有可能清算黑警嘅方法<br />\n何不將呢個製度<span style=\"color: red;\">長期化</span>？<br />\n<br />\n我嘅諗法係依家成個監警制度同埋投訴課形同垃圾<br />\n冇人可以制衡佢哋嘅決定，又冇人可以防止調查機構包庇黑警嘅原因在於冇針對監警機構嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">懲罰機制</span><br />\n<br />\n如果呢個新嘅「監警公署」係和<span style=\"color: red;\">直選議員組成嘅委員會</span>，或者<span style=\"color: red;\">退休法官組成嘅委員會</span>負責<br />\n就可能可以避免呢個情況出現<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">直選議員</span>必須要受選舉洗禮同民意監督<br />\n如果再好似依家咁包庇黑警，下次<span style=\"color: red;\">選舉必然受到選民懲罰</span><br />\n(當然，前提係香港選舉制度唔會再被侵蝕落去)<br />\n<br />\n至於<span style=\"color: red;\">退休法官</span>，佢哋包庇黑警處事不公輸嘅就會係佢哋<span style=\"color: red;\">一生公正嘅聲譽</span><br />\n(呢個懲罰唔夠制度化，但無可否認法官係大多數香港人仍然相信嘅，而且比較易吸納更大光譜嘅人)<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家點睇？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有用！ 成立監警公署<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />垃圾，咪又係變老廉"},{"pid":"e58febc504f5558e31063d4015d9c374a868a3f2","tid":1491623,"uid":171094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:24:21.000Z","msg":"大家一齊交流吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"474dc5f198d7c0b0255a9ea77fbb502a514e3c1b","tid":1491623,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:25:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ce496896b8254f826e634cb6176671b186b7bd","tid":1491623,"uid":171094,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:28:00.000Z","msg":"新機構職員唔可以係公務員<br />\n必須成個機構同政府切割<br />\n職員查完嘢都唔使驚比人寫花 appraisal<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c669f0b98a9f694569e718ef153dae004a2da4a","tid":1491623,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:29:21.000Z","msg":"終身褫奪公民權利！"},{"pid":"c7808625075e4715dcec2dc5f1898b8fdab5fc38","tid":1491623,"uid":34107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:29:21.000Z","msg":"咁只係查到警<br />\n查唔到官<br />\n查唔到警暴既因<br />\n只有獨立調查委員會先查到官"},{"pid":"c5eac40464a5a647f45bfe75169ff361b4dbb5e1","tid":1491623,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:29:55.000Z","msg":"仲洗咩證據？<br />\n今時今日我唔信仲有白警，殺哂班畜牲咪得"},{"pid":"274f6a84c240fdfa636a715e9455bad8511a2eda","tid":1491623,"uid":171094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7808625075e4715dcec2dc5f1898b8fdab5fc38","tid":1491623,"uid":34107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:29:21.000Z","msg":"咁只係查到警<br />\n查唔到官<br />\n查唔到警暴既因<br />\n只有獨立調查委員會先查到官"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:40:33.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以委員會短期內都係要繼續推<br />\n我相信人性本惡<br />\n特別係有炮嘅人好易將呢啲惡念放大<br />\n即使香港民主化咗，警隊重組咗<br />\n都一定有啲自以為是嘅毅進仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依然要有個可行嘅機制去震懾想犯法嘅黑警<br />\n比佢哋知道知法犯法唔係落地獄咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 在世都要受罰<br />\n<br />\n而制裁政治人物，長遠方法都係要靠民主化"},{"pid":"af600a9dfb1df40f67be31468efbd44facc94be0","tid":1491623,"uid":171094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:45:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a56198c4dcedd0638acc02a8b869be16aad1b5fa","tid":1491623,"uid":171094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:48:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef8d2bf82abaa52e62d24fcd2a8f601f96ec4eea","tid":1491623,"uid":289751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:50:54.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">－－－－唔好意思，借post－－－－</div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【文宣】緊急！緊急！緊急！要在九月前爭取支持香港人權與民主法案<br />\n要班仆街共享大灣區榮耀，世世代代做中國人，唔該大家入黎幫手同推post！！！</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1491251/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1491251/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"f0c8752aa762089752ec4431384d2c06557458bd","tid":1491623,"uid":171094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:59:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"325574591e64e2df6411d21538168f94c1cd7468","tid":1491623,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T14:04:01.000Z","msg":"仲要有一隊執法隊伍專門查狗捉狗"}]}